  "title": "feat(index): add child indices to UiState correctly",
  "body": "Before this change, UiState was merging the indexIds directly with the other state, meaning it's very hard to do changes like IFW-933, which filter out the current UiState, as well as making routing later more easy to write (IFW-941 specifically)\r\n\r\nMerging this will prompt an update to #4070 to have correct UiState in the tests\r\n\r\n",
